            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052401/Vandenberghe, Elseviers Dictionary of Architecture (1988)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>古典建築中，含特殊柱頂楣構且按標準構件構築的立柱群。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
